Class SuperMarket

  • java.lang.Object
    • Game_Structure.SuperMarket

  • public class SuperMarket
extends java.lang.Object
    SuperMarket Class is implemented as a View class (Project is trying to approach to Model-view-controller design pattern) This class implemented to display content of SuperMarket panel to the user and relays user command/action to the Controller.
    Author:
    Edward Wong - University of Canterbury SENG_201 15/05/2020
